Onekaka.title: Onekaka
Onekaka.byline: Onekaka is a rural district on the coast between Takaka and Collingwood in Golden Bay, at the northwestern tip of the South Island, New Zealand.

Oneonta (New York).title: Oneonta (New York)
Oneonta (New York).byline: Oneonta is in Otsego County, in Central New York.
